Date: Tue, 23 Jun 2026 20:33:39 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] fix: v0.5/v0.6 review improvements
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Filter front-matter directives (router, adapter, butuhAuth) from compiled output
- Source map V3 semicolon padding for proper line mapping
- Error boundary context enrichment (tag name instead of generic 'elemen')
- SPA event listener cleanup tracking (removeEventListener on unmount)
- Source map granularity: pass loc from key visitors to emit()
- Builder SPA: extract runtime helpers once, not per-page
- CHANGELOG typo fix: __dipasungFns → __dipasangFns
- 3 snapshot tests updated for new error context format
- 306 tests passing, 0 failed
---
